Class FileSystemBlobStrategy

  • java.lang.Object

    public class FileSystemBlobStrategy
extends Object
implements org.apache.activemq.blob.BlobUploadStrategy, org.apache.activemq.blob.BlobDownloadStrategy, ActiveMQSupport
    BlobUploadStrategy and BlobDownloadStrategy implementation which use the FileSystem to lookup the File for the BlobMessage
